aa(lp116
VWho thinks that A is true \u2014
p117
aVthat, on average, it'll take longer to see head-tail-head than head-tail-tail?
p118
aVWho thinks that B is true \u2014 that on average, they're the same?
p119
aVWho thinks that C is true \u2014 that, on average, it'll take less time
p120
aVto see head-tail-head than head-tail-tail?
p121
aVOK, who hasn't voted yet? Because that's really naughty \u2014 I said you had to.
p122
aV(Laughter)
p123
aVOK. So most people think B is true.
